title: Watch a ‘Bad Lip Reading’ of Trump’s Inauguration
text:
Watch a ‘Bad Lip Reading’ of Trump’s Inauguration Trump and Obama go head to head in Wednesday's most viral hit on YouTube Infowars.com - January 25, 2017 Comments 
Donald Trump’s presidential inauguration has been given a dose of “Bad Lip Reading”– the wildly popular YouTube channel that dubs hilarious vocals over videos. 
Watch as Trump, Obama, Pence, Hillary and many more make humorous comments to one another in the channel’s latest viral hit.
